   "html": "板垣 征四郎"
  },
  {
   "type": "title2",
   "html": "1885 － 1948"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ いたがき・せいしろう ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n陸相、関東軍参謀長、朝鮮軍司令官、「満州国」軍政部最高顧問、陸軍大将、Ａ級戦犯"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"01a.html\">一覧　（ア）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=blended%26keyword=%25E6%259D%25BF%25E5%259E%25A3%2520%25E5%25BE%2581%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%2583%258E\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　岩手県出身。陸士卒、陸大卒。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　奉天特務機関長に就任、作戦参謀<a href=\"../p/ikanji.html\">石原莞爾</a>とともに満州事変を引き起こす。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1932/03mansy.html\">「満州国」建国</a>後は満州国軍政部最高顧問、関東軍参謀長、師団長を歴任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　この間、満州拓殖株式会社を設立して移民計画を推進する。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1937/kono1_1.html\">近衛内閣①</a>の改造で陸相に就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　陸相として<a href=\"../1938/04sodoi.html\">国家総動員法</a>の追加発動、満州産業五ヶ年計画の実施に努めた。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1939/hira_1.html\">平沼内閣</a>に留任し、<a href=\"../1940/09jdi_d.html\">日独伊三国軍事同盟の締結</a>を強引に進めるが、<a href=\"../1941/06ds_ka.html\">独ソ戦</a>により挫折。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、Ａ級戦犯として<a href=\"../1948/11tokyo.html\">東京裁判で「絞首刑」の判決</a>。<a href=\"../1948/12senpa.html\">刑死</a>。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
